        {
            "reference": {
                "value": "4182084"
            },
            "heading": {
                "type": "heading",
                "content": "Deel en vergelijk",
                "level": 1
            },
            "items": [
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": "<p><span class=\"font-size-14px\">Hoera! De opdracht is nu af, bedenk met degene met wie je samen hebt gewerkt wat je wilt vertellen tijdens de presentatie.</span><br/>\n </p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-14px\">De presentatie hoeft maar 1 minuut te duren.</span></p>\n"
                }
            ],
            "sections": []
        },
        {
            "reference": {
                "value": "4182085"
            },
            "heading": {
                "type": "heading",
                "content": "Beoordeling",
                "level": 1
            },
            "items": [
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": "<p><span class=\"font-size-14px\">Je mag nu zelf deze checklist invullen om te kijken hoe goed je de opdracht hebt gedaan.<br/>\n<br/>\nVul in de tabel in:<br/>\n<br/>\n1 = niet goed<br/>\n2 = goed<br/>\n3 = Erg goed</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<table align=\"left\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"height-30-pixels width-304-pixels\">\n<p><span class=\"font-size-14px\">Heb je zelfstandig gewerkt?</span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"height-30-pixels width-28-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"height-30-pixels width-28-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"height-30-pixels width-28-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"height-30-pixels width-304-pixels\">\n<p><span class=\"font-size-14px\">Heb je je aandacht gehouden bij de opdracht?</span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"height-30-pixels width-28-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"height-30-pixels width-28-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"height-30-pixels width-28-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"height-30-pixels width-304-pixels\">\n<p><span class=\"font-size-14px\">Was je werktempo goed?</span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"height-30-pixels width-28-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"height-30-pixels width-28-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"height-30-pixels width-28-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"height-29-pixels width-304-pixels\">\n<p><span class=\"font-size-14px\">Heb je alle vragen beantwoord?</span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"height-29-pixels width-28-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"height-29-pixels width-28-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"height-29-pixels width-28-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"height-30-pixels width-304-pixels\">\n<p><span class=\"font-size-14px\">Heb je de opdracht goed begrepen?</span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"height-30-pixels width-28-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"height-30-pixels width-28-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"height-30-pixels width-28-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"height-30-pixels width-304-pixels\">\n<p><span class=\"font-size-14px\">Heb je goed samengewerkt met je klasgenoot?</span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"height-30-pixels width-28-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"height-30-pixels width-28-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"height-30-pixels width-28-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"height-30-pixels width-304-pixels\">\n<p><span class=\"font-size-14px\">Heb je een duidelijke presentatie gegeven?</span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"height-30-pixels width-28-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"height-30-pixels width-28-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"height-30-pixels width-28-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"height-30-pixels width-304-pixels\">\n<p><span class=\"font-size-14px\">Ziet de poster met je ontwerp er netjes uit?</span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"height-30-pixels width-28-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"height-30-pixels width-28-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"height-30-pixels width-28-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n"
